{"id": "1223842884017721375", "channel_id": "1223842884017721375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1079677800023347250", "author_name": "juzi6912", "author_bot": false, "content": "馬上要回去拜山，請問貓貓之前說過節日可能會出一些付費禮包，這個有在計畫內嗎？可以方便大家攢彩色抽卡石頭。\n不僅是彩色抽卡石頭，技能培養材料也沒有了，囤積材料趕不上人物養成的速度。\n希望清明前可以上架上述付費禮包。", "timestamp": "2024-03-31T03:54:41.451000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🧠", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1223842884017721375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "清明節快到了，請問有節日付費禮包嗎", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1223863657138749452", "channel_id": "1223842884017721375", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "校貓的操作非常神奇，他寧願隨便削弱隨便增強角色來讓下一個限定池的up角提高消費慾，也不願意老老實實的出禮包騙課，他真的我哭死。", "timestamp": "2024-03-31T05:17:14.149000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1223842884017721375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "清明節快到了，請問有節日付費禮包嗎", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
